%% SC-06 · AI 解析失败降级与重试 · owner=[s4] · mockup=P04+P05
flowchart TD
  Start([S4 consumer 接 wrongbook.item.created]) --> TryMain[调主 provider dashscope]
  TryMain -->|200| OK[status=completed · 发 analyzed 事件]
  TryMain -->|429| SwitchOS[Sentinel 切 openai]
  TryMain -->|5xx/超时| SwitchOS
  SwitchOS --> TryAlt[调 openai]
  TryAlt -->|200| OK
  TryAlt -->|都失败| Placeholder[status=degraded · 占位卡]
  Placeholder --> PublishAnalyzed[仍发 wrongbook.item.analyzed · payload.degraded=true]
  PublishAnalyzed --> PromptRetry[P05 显示"点击重试" CTA]
  PromptRetry --> UserRetry{用户点重试?}
  UserRetry -->|是| RetryPost[POST /ai/retry/:id]
  UserRetry -->|否| Accept[接受降级 · 加入错题本]
  RetryPost --> TryMain
